# Business Insights

## Dashboard Summary

The dashboard provides an interactive overview of sales performance using key performance indicators (KPIs), trend analysis, and visual comparisons across regions, categories, and customer segments.

## Key Insights

### 1. Sales Performance
Electronics generated the highest sales among all product categories, making it the strongest revenue contributor.

### 2. Regional Performance
The West region recorded the highest overall sales and profit, while some other regions showed comparatively lower performance.

### 3. Profitability
Sales increased at the end of the year.

### 4. Sales Trend
Sales varied over time, with noticeable periods of growth that can support seasonal planning and forecasting.

## Business Value

The dashboard helps business stakeholders:

- Monitor overall business performance.
- Compare sales and profit across categories and regions.
- Identify high-performing customer segments.
- Analyze sales trends over time.
- Support data-driven strategic decisions through interactive filtering.
